title: Pete Buttigieg, Primary Election Results
itunes:title: Pete Buttigieg, Primary Election Results
description:
Guests: Josh Wingrove, Bloomberg White House reporter, Joe Crowley, former New York Congressman and Democratic Caucus Chair, and Matt Gorman, Vice President at Targeted Victory & Former NRCC Communications Director. Kevin also spoke with former Mayor of South Bend, Indiana and former Democratic candidate for president, Pete Buttigieg about trade and the 2020 election.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
